         <h3>Annotated code</h3>
         <p>If you, like me, can't wait to experiment with the endless possibilities that using canvas on webcam images can give developers,
         this <a href="docs/camvas.html">annotated source code</a> (laid out by the invaluable <a href="http://jashkenas.github.com/docco/">Docco</a>)
         is just waiting for you - go and have a blast!</p>
        <h3>Live demo</h3>
        <p>This demo only works on the most recent versions of chrome, firefox and opera (possibly explorer too, but I would not vouch on it.)</p>
        <p>Some browser will ask you for permissions to use your webcam: accept it in order to see the demo in action</p>
